  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Beauty",
    "@type": [
      "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "A domain of products, practices, and industries related to personal care, cosmetics, skincare, and bodily appearance, often associated with aesthetic expression and identity construction."
      },
      {
        "@language": "it",
        "@value": "Ambito che comprende prodotti, pratiche e industrie legate alla cura della persona, alla cosmetica, alla skincare e all’aspetto corporeo, spesso associato all’espressione estetica e alla costruzione dell’identiteit."
      },
      {
        "@language": "nl",
        "@value": "Een domein van producten, praktijken en industrieën die verband houden met persoonlijke verzorging, cosmetica, huidverzorging en lichamelijke verschijning, vaak geassocieerd met esthetische expressie en identiteitsconstructie."
      },
      {
        "@language": "ja",
        "@value": "パーソナルケア、化粧品、スキンケア、身体的外見に関連する製品、実践、産業の領域。美的表現とアイデンティティの構築に関連することが多い。"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ru",
        "@value": "Сфера товаров, практик и индустрий, связанных с уходом за собой, косметикой и внешним видом, часто ассоциирующаяся с эстетическим самовыражением и конструированием идентичности."
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Beauty"
      },
      {
        "@language": "it",
        "@value": "Cura della persona"
      },
      {
        "@language": "nl",
        "@value": "Schoonheidsverzorging"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ja",
        "@value": "美容"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ru",
        "@value": "Красота и уход"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Region",
    "@type": [
      "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "A geographical area."
      },
      {
        "@language": "it",
        "@value": "Un'area geografica."
      },
      {
        "@language": "nl",
        "@value": "Een geografisch gebied."
      },
      {
        "@language": "ja",
        "@value": "地理的区域。"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ru",
        "@value": "Географическая область (регион)."
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Region"
      },
      {
        "@language": "it",
        "@value": "Regione"
      },
      {
        "@language": "nl",
        "@value": "Regio"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ja",
        "@value": "地域"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ru",
        "@value": "Регион"
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#subClassOf": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Location"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/Collection",
    "@type": [
      "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "A set of entities grouped together, either explicitly or implicitly, based on perceived coherence, curation, or shared associations. Collections function as the primary means through which an Aesthetic is expressed and recognized, without requiring fixed or exhaustive membership."
      },
      {
        "@language": "it",
        "@value": "Un insieme di entità raggruppate assieme, in modo esplicito o implicito, per coerenza percepita o associazioni condivise. Le collezioni costituiscono il mezzo primario tramite il quale le estetiche vengono espresse o riconosciute; non richiedono la fissità o l'esausività dei loro membri."
      },
      {
        "@language": "nl",
        "@value": "Een verzameling entiteiten die expliciet of impliciet zijn samengevoegd op basis van waargenomen coherentie, curatie of gedeelde associaties. Collecties fungeren als het primaire middel waarmee een esthetiek wordt uitgedrukt en herkend, zonder dat een vast of uitputtend lidmaatschap vereist is."
      },
      {
        "@language": "ja",
        "@value": "一貫性、共通の連想に基づいて明示的・暗黙的にキュレーションされた実体の集合。美学が具体的に表現・認識されるための主要な媒体。コレクションの構成要素は必ずしも固定的や網羅的である必要はなく、流動的で変動的である。"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ru",
        "@value": "Набор сущностей, сгруппированных вместе (явно или неявно) на основе воспринимаемой целостности, кураторства или общих ассоциаций. Коллекции служат основным средством выражения и узнавания эстетики, не требуя при этом фиксированного или исчерпывающего состава участников."
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Collection"
      },
      {
        "@language": "it",
        "@value": "Collezione"
      },
      {
        "@language": "nl",
        "@value": "Collectie"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ja",
        "@value": "コレクション"
      },
      {
        "@language": "ru",
        "@value": "Коллекция"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@id": "https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/representativenessType",
    "@type": [
      "http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#DatatypeProperty"
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#domain": [
      {
        "@id": "https://w3id.org/vibe-ontology/RepresentativeAssociation"
      }
    ],
